    ModelMeshServing[ModelMesh Serving Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelMeshServing -->|state management<br/>2379/TCP HTTP| etcd[etcd v3.5.4+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMeshServing -->|model storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| S3[S3/Minio Storage<br/>REQUIRED]
    ModelMeshServing -->|CRD reconciliation<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelMeshServing -.->|webhook TLS certs<br/>Certificate CRDs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ModelMeshServing -.->|metrics collection<br/>ServiceMonitor CRD| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.55+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    ModelMeshServing -.->|CRD compatibility<br/>InferenceService| KServe[KServe<br/>INTERNAL RHOAI]
    ModelMeshServing -->|S3-compatible storage<br/>model artifacts| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>INTERNAL RHOAI]

    %% Internal RHOAI Integrations (Optional)
    ModelMeshServing -.->|mTLS encryption<br/>traffic routing| ServiceMesh["Service Mesh - Istio<br/>INTERNAL RHOAI OPTIONAL"]
    ModelMeshServing -.->|UI management<br/>namespace config| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL RHOAI]

    %% Built-in Runtime Support
    ModelMeshServing -->|model format support| Triton[Triton Inference Server<br/>tensorflow, pytorch, onnx, tensorrt]
    ModelMeshServing -->|model format support| MLServer[MLServer<br/>sklearn, xgboost, lightgbm]
    ModelMeshServing -->|model format support| OpenVINO[OpenVINO Model Server<br/>openvino_ir, onnx]
    ModelMeshServing -->|model format support| TorchServe[TorchServe<br/>pytorch]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -.->|scrapes metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS| ModelMeshServing
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes runtime metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP| ModelMeshServing

